PISTACHIO PUDDING CAKE

1 pkg white cake mix              1/2 cup finely chopped walnuts
1 pkg instant pistachio pudding   1/2 cup oil
1 cup club soda                   4 eggs

Blend eggs, oil and club soda.  Add cake mix
and pudding.  Beat until creamy.  Add chopped nuts.
Preheat oven to 350 degrees.  Bake in a greased
and floured tube pan 45 to 50 minutes.

Topping:

1 pt heavy cream              2 tsp sugar
1 pkg instant pistachio pudding
3/4 cup milk

Mix all together and beat until creamy.



